{
  "texts": [
    "The final state is calculated after the scheduling decision is added.",
    "It is then processed by the DES DES.",
    "A new intermediate state is calculated, an intermediate reward is generated, and new observations are passed to the agent.",
    "This process is iterated until all movable stations are placed.",
    "Afterward, the action of the scheduler is, together with the accumulated actions of the layout planner, fed back to the DES."
  ]
}